<p class="p1"><span class="s1">11.&nbsp;Discounts<br /> </span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span class="s1">11.1 Go4sightseeing Credits<br /> <br /> </span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">11.1.1 Go4sightseeing Credits are points that are awarded to you and will be accumulated in your Go4sightseeing Account until expiry. Points are awarded on the actual participated and unrefunded activities purchased from Go4sightseeing&rsquo;s platforms, based on the award program at the time of purchase. Every Ten (10) Go4sightseeing Points carries a value of Hong Kong ONE Dollar (HKD1.00) and the conversion of these Hong Kong Dollar denominated points are based on the exchange rate Go4sightseeing used on the date of your redemption. These points can be used to redeem any of our products on our platform or to reduce the total check out price.</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">11.1.2 The Go4sightseeing&rsquo;s Credits may be obtained through the following means and the amount of credit received may vary with each purchase and is at the sole discretion of Go4sightseeing&rsquo;s:<br /> </span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">(a) Rebates from previous purchases</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">(b) Receiving the credit through any authorized means, determined at Go4sightseeing&rsquo;s discretion</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">(c) Upon submitting the review after successfully completing Go4sightseeing&rsquo;s experience you purchased (not applicable to activities priced at 0, such as free vouchers)</span></p>
<p class="p3" style="padding-left: 60px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">11.1.3 If you've completed the same activity more than once in the same month, you will only get credits for the first review you leave for that activity.</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">11.1.4 All Go4sightseeing Credits obtained anytime in the first calendar year will expire on the last day of the next calendar year. Therefore, if you are awarded the credit on 1 October 2017, your credits will expire and therefore be removed from your account on 31 December 2018. All the credits accumulated to date as of 25 September 2017, regardless of when you obtained the credits and is remained unused will be expired on 31 December 2018.</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 30px;"><span class="s1"> <br /> <br /> </span></p>
