<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">11.2.1 Go4sightseeing Coupons are coupons with a one-time use that will be sent to your designated email address or applied directly to your Go4sightseeing Account, which may be used in exchange for discounts off future bookings on the Go4sightseeing Booking Platform.</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span class="s1">11.2.2 Go4sightseeing Credits may be attained through the following means:<br /> </span></p>
